{"tid":1715354,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"上水 元朗 癈老出動","createTime":"2019-11-13T05:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T05:29:59.000Z","uid":215924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39bb491f3efa1206fda26846346c512767637cd2","tid":1715354,"uid":215924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"示威者連日多區堵路，今早元朗、上水均出現黑衣示威者被不同政見市民攻擊的情況。其中在上水，數十名身穿普通裝束的市民拾起路面上的磚塊，不停擲向黑衣示威者並大叫「死曱甴走啦！」示威者被迫撐傘後退；元朗亦有黑衣少女受襲頭部受傷流血，要受治理，其中一人大叫「手足走先啦」，呼籲其他示威者為保安全，先行離開。<br />\n<br />\n影片來源：網上片段（上水）、讀者提供（元朗）<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2613097125442558/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2613097125442558%2F&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLad6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=a5b0df66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2613097125442558/</a><br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"1732078c91693830cb44c6d294852448c351b3e7","tid":1715354,"uid":215924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"03e1cf4430df109106b2fec1012abec5d265cd8b","tid":1715354,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"朝早人唔多 <br />\n聚左一堆番工廢老<br />\n係危險"}]}